\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{x}\approx c_{1}\vec{v}_{1}+c_{2}\vec{v}_{2}
\]

\end_inset

for some 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{2}$
\end_inset

.
