\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}c_{1}\vec{v}_{1}+\lambda_{2}c_{2}\vec{v}_{2}=\lambda_{1}\left(c_{1}\vec{v}_{1}+\frac{\lambda_{2}}{\lambda_{1}}c_{2}\vec{v_{2}}\right),$
